已经又预订了周四周五的房间了！', '2024-04-17', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'', ''公共设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236r12000dpfu6i4A53A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233112000dpfjry2107E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234s12000dpfup1tA0FC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236l12000dpftr92DBEC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231912000dpfmmv3138C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '相当的满意', '相当的满意', '2024-10-03', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233912000fxzaswwA1EF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234512000fxyxi834267_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236a12000fy09iz18EEE_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231o12000fy07byj0D2B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232h12000fxzz8zj498C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233s12000fxzpe431C94_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店非常满意，下次来广州还会入住花园酒店?。酒店是可以好好逛逛的，这两天广州天天', '酒店非常满意，下次来广州还会入住花园酒店?。酒店是可以好好逛逛的，这两天广州天天下雨，入住这里正好可以在雨天的时候在酒店逛一下。

